      "title": "Claude Code as a Daily Driver: Claude.md, Skills, Subagents, Plugins, and MCPs",
      "url": "https://arps18.github.io/posts/claude-code-mastery/",
      "discuss_url": "https://news.ycombinator.com/item?id=48289950",
      "score": 206,
      "comments": 164,
      "author": "arps18",
      "published": "2026-05-27T05:13:39Z",
      "bullets": [
        "Anthropic's Claude Code CLI leverages the Model Context Protocol (MCP) to integrate external data sources and tools into developer workflows.",
        "Developers use subagents and custom skills to delegate complex, multi-step coding tasks while maintaining fine-grained control over execution.",
        "Structuring project-specific guidelines in Claude.md files steers agent behavior, ensuring compliance with local coding standards and architecture."
      ]
    },
    {
      "source": "lobsters",
